casebody.data:
Katherine KESSEL-REVIS, petitioner,
v.
TEXAS. No. 15-6673. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 11, 2016.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed *875until February 1, 2016, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
